# =============================================
# Savage-Sun-Setting - Optimized .dockerignore
# =============================================

# === Ignore everything by default (safety) ===
**

# === Explicitly ALLOW only what we need ===
!*.sln
!*.csproj
!Dockerfile
!.dockerignore
!Directory.Build.props
!Directory.Packages.props
!global.json

# Allow source code for all projects
!src/**/*
!tests/**/*

# Allow necessary config files (examples only)
!**/appsettings.json.example
!**/appsettings.*.example
!**/README.md
!**/LICENSE

# =============================================
# Explicitly IGNORE large/unnecessary items
# =============================================

# Build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/PublishOutput/
**/App_Data/

# IDE / temporary files
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.sln.user
**/.rider/

# Secrets & sensitive files
**/appsettings.json
**/appsettings.*.json
**/.user-secrets/
**/.aws/
**/*.pfx
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# Large data files (your lore PDFs!)
**/*.pdf
**/attachments/
**/lore-*.pdf

# Package caches
**/packages/
**/*.nupkg
**/node_modules/

# Git
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Docker
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore
Dockerfile.*

# Logs & temp
**/*.log
**/logs/
**/tmp/

# OS junk
**/.DS_Store
**/*.swp
**Thumbs.db